'''''Star Wars Summer Special'' 1983''' was a comic book released in the United Kingdom that reprinted the UK-original stories [[The Empire Strikes Back Monthly 149|''The Empire Strikes Back Monthly'' 149]], ''[[The Pandora Effect]]'', ''[[Rust Never Sleeps]]'' and ''[[The Flight of the Falcon]]''.

The stories were originally published in UK in ''[[The Empire Strikes Back Monthly 149]], [[The Empire Strikes Back Monthly 151|151]], [[The Empire Strikes Back Monthly 156|156]] and [[The Empire Strikes Back Monthly 157|157]].

